# Agent Behavior

- Each time when a specific task is given, don't overstep from your role. Always ask to confirm next steps before processing.
- Prefer direct tool calls (Read, Grep, Glob) over Task subagents for codebase exploration to minimize latency.
- During the planning stage always check rules and never modify any source files. You can only modify your plan files.